SUMMARY:COX ASSET MEXICO SA DE C V — Virtual Fixed Income Investor Call
DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm timing and availability\n\n
 Virtual fixed income investor call coordinated by Deutsche Bank Securities
 . Part of a series commencing April 28\, 2026.\nIssuer: COX ASSET MEXICO S
 A DE C V\nRoadshow: URL: https://dealroadshow.com | Entry Code: COX2026 | 
 Direct Link: https://dealroadshow.com/e/COX2026\n\nDeal context:\nCox Asse
 t Mexico\, SA de CV — a special purpose vehicle created by Cox ABG Group\,
  SA to acquire Iberdrola México\, SA de CV — has mandated Barclays\, Citig
 roup\, Deutsche Bank Securities\, and Goldman Sachs as Global Coordinators
  and Joint Bookrunners\, alongside BBVA\, Santander\, and Scotiabank as Jo
 int Bookrunners\, for a dual-tranche USD-denominated 144A/Reg S Senior Sec
 ured Notes offering. The deal is expected to consist of a long 5-year and 
 a 10-year benchmark-sized tranche with expected ratings of BBB- (Fitch) an
 d Ba1 (Moody's)\, with investor calls commencing Tuesday\, April 28\, 2026
 \, subject to market conditions. This is an acquisition financing SPV deal
  with a split rating straddling the IG/HY boundary.
